      h1 I Know AP: The Transformative Power of MCP
      h2.subheading.mb-3 Understanding MCP's Role in Business Adaptation
      .card.mb-4.shadow-sm
        .card-header.d-flex.align-items-center
          i.bi.bi-youtube.me-2
          h5.mb-0 Deep Dive Podcast: The Transformative Power of MCP
        .card-body
          p.
            Explore the transformative impact of the Model Context Protocol (MCP) on AI agents in this insightful episode by the Deep Dive team. Learn how MCP enables real-time learning, dynamic adaptability, and seamless workflow integration, redefining the role of AI in business and beyond.
          .ratio.ratio-16x9
            iframe(src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/W1ehT3Qgyyo?si=1GSrT3mlLGhfjE5B"
              title="Deep Dive Podcast: The Transformative Power of MCP" frameborder="0"
              allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
